<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #179299; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>All out of credits!</h1>

    <p>You've used all your episode credits on PodRead. Looks like you're getting a lot out of it!</p>

    <p>Grab another credit pack whenever you're ready. Credits never expire, and packs start at $9.99 for 5 episodes.</p>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= @billing_url %>" class="button">Buy more credits</a>
    </p>

    <p>Thanks for using PodRead!</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
